---
/** Placeholder until real client stories are approved — no fabricated quotes. */
---

<section
  class="scroll-mt-24 border-y border-sand/60 bg-linen py-20 sm:py-24"
  aria-labelledby="stories-heading"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 text-center sm:px-8">
    <p class="reveal eyebrow">Client stories</p>
    <h2
      id="stories-heading"
      class="reveal reveal-delay-1 mt-4 font-display text-3xl text-ink sm:text-4xl"
    >
      Voices from the journey
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 prose-width mx-auto mt-6 text-pretty text-muted">
      Testimonials from clients will appear here as they are shared. If you have
      worked with Ashley and would like to contribute a brief reflection, please
      reach out directly.
    </p>
    <div
      class="reveal reveal-delay-3 mx-auto mt-10 max-w-md rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-sand bg-cream/80 px-8 py-10"
    >
      <p class="font-display text-lg italic text-loam">
        Stories coming soon
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">
        We share only authentic experiences — never placeholder reviews.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
